  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Box
    A pair of coordinates, defining an immutable box.
    Coordinate
    An immutable co-ordinate
    MapProvider
    An abstract class that is extended to provide support for loading and saving Map objects through different methods (network, disk IO, magical ponies, etc).
    World
    A data model for a singular World, containing a Map and a collection of Items and Entities.
    WorldProvider
    Basic WorldProvider class for providing Maps and Worlds.
    WorldProviderManager
    WorldProviderManager handles the main providing of Worlds, by delegating the provideWorld() method to the correct abstraction, such as IOWorldProvider, default WorldProvider, magicalPonyWorldProvider(), etc.
